snippet.title: Gunnhildr Launch - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gunnhildr now available on Steam Early Access: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1377030/Gunnhildr/

Join Our Community:
Dev Discord: www.discord.gg/gunnhildr
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GunnhildrGame

Gunnhildr is a narrative shooter set in a Norse-inspired sci-fi world. Defy the gods and give Niflheim new life through fast paced first person combat in an ever-changing world full of powers and stories to uncover.
